('201412160131444', '201412160114215', '1st MEETING OF CENTRAL COMMITTEE REGARDING CENTENARY CELEBRATIONS', '<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">MINUTES OF THE MEETING OF CENTRAL COMMITTEE REGARDING CENTENARY CELEBRATIONS</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>A meeting of the Vice-Chancellor with the members of the subject committee held on 19-11-2014 at 10:00 a.m in Main Committee Room of Islamia College, Peshawar.</p>\r\n<p>After recitation from the Holy Quran, Mr. Ajmal Khan, Vice- Chancellor, ICP welcomed all the participants in the meeting. He threw light on the importance of this up-coming mega event to &nbsp;be held in the month of March 2015 and ask everyone to fully contribute in this event for its success. Thereafter, Mr. Abaseen Yousafzai being secretary of the central committee gave a detailed presentation to the participants.</p>\r\n<p>After discussion on each and every point, following unanimous decisions for formation of committees and other essential preparatory arrangements with regard to Centenary Celebrations were made as under:-</p>\r\n<p><strong>Central Committee</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>The Vice-Chancellor, ICP&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Convener</li>\r\n    <li>Coordinator ,Inter studies, ICP</li>\r\n    <li>Principal, ICG</li>\r\n    <li>Principal, ICS</li>\r\n    <li>Secretary General, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Vice-President, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Nisar Muhammad Nisar, Executive Member, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Fayyaz Ahmad Khan, Executive Member, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Treasurer , ICP</li>\r\n    <li>Director of works, ICP</li>\r\n    <li>Administrative officer, ICP</li>\r\n    <li>Director of Sports, ICP</li>\r\n    <li>&nbsp;Registrar, ICP(Member/Observer)</li>\r\n    <li>Chief Organizer KSS &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Secretary</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Publicity Committee</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Prof.Dr.Abdus Salam Khalis, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (English)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Coordinator</li>\r\n    <li>Dr.Toqeer Alam&nbsp; (Media Officer)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Javed Iqbal, (English)</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Mohammad Abbas, (Urdu)</li>\r\n    <li>Ms. Humaira, (ICG)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Faisal Shahzad (Law)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Ateeq-ur-Rehman (English)</li>\r\n    <li>Web Administrator</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Registration &amp; Invitation Committee</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Lt. Col(R) Jamil Ahmad<em>, </em><em>Secretary General, SAA</em> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Coordinator</li>\r\n    <li>Prof. Dr. Naeem Khalid, (Physics)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Mr.Arbab Safir Ahmad, (Physics) &amp; Executive Member, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Sikandar Khan, DSA</li>\r\n    <li>Dr.Shazia Yaseen, (Physics)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Muhammad Zaman Khan, Vice- President, SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Mr.Attaullah Khan, (Comp. Science)</li>\r\n    <li>Registrar, or his Nominee&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Accommodation, Transportation, Food &amp; Hospitality Committee</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Provost &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Coordinator</li>\r\n    <li>Prof. Dr. Nisar Muhammad&nbsp; (Theology)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Prof. Eid-Ur-Rehman, Executive Committee SAA</li>\r\n    <li>Syed Kamal (Deputy Provost)</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Imtiaz Khan,(Director Transport)</li>\r\n    <li>Qazi Ubaid Ur Rehman, (Theology)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr.Hakeem Khan, Finance Secretary, SAA (Geography)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Decoration, Entertainment &amp; KSS Committee</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Prof. Dr. Syed Inayat Ali Shah, (Dean Faculty of Physical &amp; Numerical Sciences)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Coordinator</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. &nbsp;Shabir Ahmad, Principal, ICS&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Prof.Dr. Madiha Asghar, (Psychology)</li>\r\n    <li>Engineer Muhammad Abid Kamal, (Director of Works)</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Anwar Hussain, (Administrative Officer)</li>\r\n    <li>&nbsp;Khyber Students\' Societies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Security &amp; Management Committee</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Mr.Javed Iqba, (Chief Proctor) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Coordinator</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Anwar Hussain, (Administrative Officer)</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Shabir Ahmad, (Chemistry )</li>\r\n    <li>Mr. Irfan Ullah Kamran Marwat, DPE</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Sadaf Manzoor, (Statistics)</li>\r\n    <li>Ms.Sadaf Ambareen, (Urdu)</li>\r\n    <li>Dr. Muradullah, (Mathematics)</li>\r\n    <li>Commandant, CPC or his nominee</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Note:-</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">A Coordinator of the committee can opt any person from faculty or administration in the committee on consent to play his or her role in the success of the event, also if someone voluntarily offers him or herself in any of the above committees for betterment be given chance.</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p>At the end of the meeting the Vice-Chancellor reiterated for cooperation, assistance and patronage of everyone for making the functions bright and colorful. A Coordinator of the committee can opt any person from faculty or administration in the committee on consent to play his or her role in the success of the event, also if someone voluntarily offer&nbsp; him or herself in any above committee for betterment be given a chance.</p>\r\n<p>He further said that preparatory meetings of Central Committee will be held on Thursday of every 1<sup>st</sup> and 3<sup>rd</sup> week of the month at 11:00 a.m in main committee room of the University till the execution of Centenary Celebrations. Hence, next meeting will be convened on December 04, 2014 at 11:00 a.m.</p>\r\n<p>The meeting was ended with a vote of thanks from and to the Chair.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>Recorded by,</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Asst. Registrar ( Estt:<strong>)</strong></p>', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28'),
('201412160132474', '201412160114215', '2nd MEETING OF CENTRAL COMMITTEE REGARDING CENTENARY CELEBRATIONS', '<p align=\"center\">A meeting of the Vice-Chancellor with the members of the subject committee held on&nbsp; 04-12-2014 at 11:00 a.m in the office of Vice-Chancellor Office of Islamia College, Peshawar.</p>\r\n<p>After recitation from the Holy Quran, the Registrar, Prof. Dr. Sareer Badshah welcomed all the participants in the meeting. The Chair, Mr. Ajmal Khan, worthy Vice-Chancellor joined during the proceedings owing to his engagement in the ASRB meeting. Mr. M.S Abaseen Yousafzai being secretary of the central committee &amp; sub-committees gave a presentation on so for progress made and future planning regarding Centenary Celebrations.( i.e 19,20 &amp; 21 March 2014)</p>\r\n<p><strong>After discussion, following unanimous decisions were made for compliance:-</strong></p>\r\n<p>T-20/ T-10 Cricket Match &nbsp;(Pakistan- A&nbsp; VS&nbsp; Afghanistan-B) will played on March 19-2015 at Arbab Niaz Cricket Stadium/ ICS Cricket ground and the purpose of this match is fund raising ,Publicity of&nbsp; the cause, Entertainment, gathering of all old and existing students&nbsp; through&nbsp; tickets. In February 2015 tickets selling will be started. Registrar Office in coordination with Senior Alumni will approach PCB for the arrangement/correspondence of this event viz-e-viz Chief Guest Mr. Imran Khan and Guest of Honour Mr. Pervaiz Khan Khattak for day 1<sup>st</sup>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Vice-Chancellor asked that Governor/Chancellor, ICP along with other dignitaries will also be invited in centenary celebrations.</p>\r\n<p>A letter for arrangement of Khattak Dance will be sent to Inspector General Frontier Crop.</p>\r\n<p>All Print/Electronic Media will be contacted to give maximum coverage to this event.</p>\r\n<p>Senior Alumni will arrange a march of ex-Islamians, who retired from Pakistan Army.</p>\r\n<p>Mr. S.M Abaseen Yousafzai along with member of purchase committee will go to Lahore to procure gift items for the said event.&nbsp; He will contact Gowns making experts to provide samples for Vice-Chancellor approval. He will also be responsible to arrange temporary stall during the event and a permanent stall for selling Gift items like: Jackets T-shirts, P-caps, Neck Ties, Sticking monograms, Hand bands, Track suits, Hand kerchiefs, Purses (male + female),Mobile pouches, Burqa clips (brooches),Key chains, Key purses and Pens.</p>\r\n<p>Lt.Col &reg; Jameel Ahmed, General Secretary Senior Alumni gave a brief presentation on Annual Calendar and Advertisement expenses, after modifications in Colander.&nbsp; The Vice-Chancellor, asked that the Colander for correct English will be vetted from Mr. Javed Iqbal, Asst. Professor, Department of English.</p>\r\n<p>As already decided next meeting will be held on December 18,2015, all members of central committees and sub-committees will be invited and the worthy Vice-Chancellor will see the progress made until then.</p>\r\n<p>The meeting was ended with a vote of thanks from and to the Chair.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Recorded By</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Asst. Registrar (E)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28'),
('201412160134044', '201412160114215', 'Registration for Centenary Celebration ', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://icp.edu.pk/images/notic_board/registration_centenary_celbration_form.pdf\">Click here to download registration form</a></p>\r\n', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28'),
('201412160325244', '201412160324106', 'DSA Introduction', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Introduction</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">This Directorate is dealing with the general problems of students which usually start from the Registration of individual student and ended on his Migration to other College / University before or after completion of his course work in ICP.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">The details of registered students are as under:</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Inter-Studies &nbsp;&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3200</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">BS 4-Year &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2684</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">MA/M.Sc &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1400</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">M.Phil / MS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; =&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 220 </span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Ph.D &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 08&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Total &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; =&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (7512)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28');
