('201412230401016', '201412230354174', 'Management Science Event Coordinator Message', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\"><img src=\"images/stories/eventcoordinatormsg.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">It is very important for students of any field of education to attend seminars and workshops</span> <span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">to enhance their knowledge. Workshops and seminars give us a unique opportunity to hear experts in our field and get advice from some of the most successful professionals.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">In addition, participating in such events is great for networking. Seminars and workshops are</span> <span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">a way to meet others in a field and obtain valuable contacts. There, we are able to share </span><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">information, experiences, problems and solutions with professionals that have been in our</span> <span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">place. Actually, attending seminars broaden our horizons.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Realizing the importance of seminars, workshops and conferences, Management Science Department&nbsp; of Islamia College is always striving to arrange such events at least once a month to groom its students.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Asia Umar Khan</span></strong></em></p>', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28');
