/11</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 105.15pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color black black -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\">Mrs. Badia Raza,</span></p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\">Regional Head North, ICAP House</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 1.2in; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color black black -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"115\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Khyber Union Hall, ICUP</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Summary:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">The seminar was organized by the Management Sciences department of Islamia College University in which the Regional Head North of Institute of Chartered Accountants of Pakistan, Mrs.Badia Raza threw light on the bright prospects of selecting Chartered Accountancy as a profession. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Objectives of the Seminar</span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\"> The main objective of the program was to facilitate the students in making their appropriate career choice and to create awareness of the profession of the accountancy to them.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Other underlying objectives were :</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">To broaden the professional vision of the students.</span></li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">To tell the students about the eligibility criteria for admission in ICAP.</span></span></li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">To motivate the students by telling them the monetary and social benefits of learning at ICAP.</span></span></li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">To remove their ambiguities about the admission and academic complexities in ICAP. </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Chief Guest</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Mrs.Badia Raza, The Regional Head North, ICAP House.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Organized By</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Department of Management Science, ICUP.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Presided by</span