olid solid none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color black black -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: verdana,geneva; color: #000000;\">Dr. Javed Iqbal,Senior Instructor,Pakistan Assiciation of Rural Development (PARD)</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 1.2in; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color black black -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"115\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; color: #000000; font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Khyber Union Hall, ICUP</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Summary:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">The seminar was organized by the Management Sciences department of Islamia College University in which the Senior Instructor of Pakistan Association of Rural Development(PARD),Dr.Javed Iqbal, delivered a speech on career planning and development for the students&rsquo; proper guidance. Dr. Javed Iqbal, having his Ph.D in philosophy, advised the students to develop the three most important features in their personalities i.e. Intelligence Quotient(IQ), Educational Quotient(EQ) and Common Quotient(CQ) to have a brilliant future in their life. A large gathering of students of B.B.A., M.B.A., and faculty members attended this interesting and informational seminar.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Objectives of the Seminar:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">The main objective of the seminar was to guide the students for proper career planning and development. Other underlying objectives were :</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n    <ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n        <ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n            <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">To guide the students in building a fair and disciplined personality.</span></li>\r\n            <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">To tell them the benefits and importance of being just and fair in daily life and career.</span></li>\r\n            <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">To tell them the techniques of selecting a suitable career.</span></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Chief Guest:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Dr. Javed Iqbal, Senior Instructor, Pakistan Association of Rural Development (PARD).</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Organized By:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Department of Management Science, ICUP.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Presided by:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Dr.Qadar Bakhsh Baloach,Chairman Department of Management Sciences ,ICUP.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Attended By:</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Students of M.B.A and B.B.A, and faculty members of management science department.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Events Sequence of the Seminar:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Main events of the seminar were as following.</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Welcome note by&nbsp; Event coordinator, Ms.Asia Umar Khan, lecturer Management Science Department, ICUP </span></li>\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Recitation of the Holy Quran by&nbsp; Waqas Ahmad, student of B.B.A 6th.</span></li>\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Lecture by Dr. Javed Iqbal, Senior Instructor, Pakistan Association of Rural Development (PARD) with multimedia presentation</span></li>\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Questions and answers session&nbsp; between&nbsp; students and the speaker.</span></li>\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">A thanking speech by Dr Qadir Bakhsh Baloach,Chairman Department of Management Sciences.</span></li>\r\n        <li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;\">Interactive session and tea.</span></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'General ', 55, 0, '2015-10-28');
INSERT INTO `artical` (`art_id`, `cat_id`, `art_title`, `art_detail`, `art_cat`, `sort`, `status`, `art_date`) VALUES
('201412230407166', '201412230354174', 'Management Science Workshops', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 12pt;\">3-Days Workshop on</span></strong><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 12pt;\">Integrated Approach to Business Research</span></strong><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 12pt;\">For Students of MS/M.Phil</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Summary:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Today higher education Higher education is being driven by research activities, with more and more attention and resources being diverted towards quality research, the need to research have never been strong for university students. For this very reason a workshop was held for MS/M.Phil students where they could learn the basic and medium level techniques on how to carry out their research project, with specific focus on the wide ranging quantitative techniques that form an essential part of the final dissertation.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Objectives</span>:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">To learn mechanics of writing a Research Proposal with special emphases on the following:</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_bullet_small\">\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Identification &amp; formulation of statement of the problem and generating research question (s).</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Developing a detailed understanding on writing a critical review from the related literature.</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Formulating research hypotheses through conceptual mapping and establishing its relationship to the data analysis.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Enhancing capacity building amongst researcher in quantitative data analyses through SPSS hands-on-training</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Develop an understanding on how to format a research report</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva;\">Resource Persons</span></strong>:</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul_star\">\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Dr. Qadar Bakhsh Baloch Director Higher studies &amp; Research , Islamia College University, Peshawar</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Dr Sareer Badshah, Chairman, Department of Statistics, Islamia College University Peshawar</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Mr. Khawaja Fawad Latif (Lecturer, City University of Science and Information Technology)</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Mr. Aamir Nadeem (Assistant Professor, City University of Science and Information Technology)</span></li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 8pt;\">Session Coordinator: Mr. Muhammad Usman Haider, PhD Research Scholar, Abasyn University, Peshawar.</span>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 63.45pt; border: 1pt